com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.method
Interface NativeDirectStaticMethodCallback

All Superinterfaces:
NativeBehavior, NativeCallback, NativeCapable, NativeDirectCallback, NativeDirectMethodCallback, NativeMethod, NativeMethodCallback, NativeStaticMethod, NativeStaticMethodCallback
public interface NativeDirectStaticMethodCallback
extends NativeDirectMethodCallback, NativeStaticMethodCallback

The NativeDirectStaticMethodCallback is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible static Java methods from native. The Java methods are NOT called using Java reflection.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
